<para>
  &kwordquiz; provides the ability to print vocabulary documents in several different ways. When selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Print...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> you are presented with the standard &kde; print dialog. In order to get access to the special &kwordquiz; features you need to click on the <guibutton>Options&gt;&gt;</guibutton> to see the <guilabel>Vocabulary Options</guilabel> tab. On this tab you can select to print the document as a vocabulary list (&ie; as displayed in the editor), a vocabulary exam, or as flashcards.
</para>
